    {
      "class": "TextView",
      "text": "This is a paragraph or two where you explain what your product is. Do not get into too much detail.  You will have a chance to get into details in the subsequent sections.  \n\nHere, just help the reader understand what your product is, and a little bit about your vision for the product.",
