    {
      "class": "TextView",
      "text": "This is the place to be more precise about your product. Mention what the product is. Is it a website? A physical store? A widget or a mobile app?      \n\nWhy should the company exist? Does it entertain? Does it make someone feel better?  Does it solve a problem for someone?  Does it teach something? What is the benefit of this company?      \n\nIn this section, help the reader understand why your company needs to exist in the world.",
      "resource_id": "product_text",
      "bounds": [
        0,
        1332,
        1440,
        2088
      ],
      "clickable": false,
      "semantic_label": null
    },
    {
      "class": "TextView",
      "text": "3) WHAT STAGE ARE YOU IN?",
